== Research Interests
Broadly speaking, I am interested in solving problems that arise in practical systems, especially 
wireless networks,  
using tools from information theory, optimization theory and statistics. Some specific research 
topics include:

- Cooperative diversity in wireless networks
- Distributed machine learning with communication constraints
- Mobile edge computing and vehicular network
- High dimensional statistical inference

